.claude/

# Finder / iCloud "2" conflict duplicates (e.g. "Foo 2.swift").
# These byte-identical copies break the build with "invalid redeclaration"
# errors. If you genuinely need a file whose basename ends in " 2", rename
# it — this pattern is purely a macOS filesystem artifact.
*\ 2.swift
*\ 2.yml
*\ 2.yaml
